    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            <h3 class="text-center">How do I make an account?</h3>
            <p class="text-center">You are required to fill out a quick application confirming your identity to join Marine, this is done to prevent bots and other malicious players from joining. Click the button below to fill out an application.</p>
            <p class="text-center">
                <a href="/auth/application" class="btn btn-primary">Create Application</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container bg-dark text-light container-one">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
