            <p class="text-center">Marine is a Pekora Revival owned and managed by the developers of Silverium Reborn and AFTERWORLD, It is one of the friendliest Pekora revivals as of right now.</p>
			<p class="text-center text-danger">NOTE: Marine is not directly affiliated with Pekora or the owner (supra) in any way, shape or form, Marine is just a community-made Pekora Rehost being managed and owned by known individuals and trusteds within the Pekora Community.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container-one bg-dark text-light">
    <div class="container container-one">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h3 class="mb-4">What makes this place different?</h3>
                <div class="row mt-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="col-2 col-md-1">
                        <h1 class="text-center">ðŸ”‘</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-10 col-md-11">
                        <p><span class="fw-bolder">No invite key required. </span>You don't need to be in the right friend group, constantly track discord servers, or buy keys from people - all you have to do is fill out an application to join.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container bg-dark text-light container-one">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            <h3>Privacy Taken Seriously.</h3>
            <ul class="selling-points">
                <li>
                    <span class="fw-bolder">You don't have to provide any personal information. </span>The only thing we ask for during the application process is a link to your profile on a social media website such as Twitter or YouTube - this is only done to verify that you are not trying to abuse the site.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="fw-bolder">Secure game servers. </span>Our game server software has been modified to not directly see the IPs of players connecting to them. This is done with the help of Quilkin. Quilkin acts as a proxy between the players and our game servers. When a player connects, Quilkin forwards the request to our VPS, which is then processed by Quilkin. The game server program only receives a local IP address from Quilkin, not the player's direct IP address. This means that even if a severe vulnerability is discovered in our game server software, attackers will not be able to collect the IP addresses of users.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="fw-bolder">IP Addresses are hashed and only stored temporarily. </span>Your IP is only stored in a hashed format when you perform certain actions, and it is not directly linked with your website account. Your IP is only ever saved for a maximum of 24 hours, after which it is deleted automatically from where it is stored (Redis - IPs are deleted once they expire, which can be between 5 minutes and 24 hours depending on the task you perform).
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
